DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

94-2254. Cincinnati Bar Assn. v. Sullivan.

This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing of respondent’s motion to withdraw motion for hearing. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that respondent’s motion be, and is hereby, granted.

IT IS FURTHER ORDERED, sua sponte, by the court that the show cause order of November 9, 1995, be vacated, and that this cause be referred to the Office of the Attorney General for collection.

Stratton, J., not participating.
